gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Lakers 101, 76ers 94
gameRecap.excerpt: The Lakers defeated the 76ers, 101-94. Anthony Davis led the way with 23 points, 19 rebounds, four assists, and four blocks for the Lakers, with LeBron James adding 20 points, eight rebounds, and six assists in the victory. Tyrese Maxey tallied 27 points, three assists, and three steals for the 76ers in the defeat. The Lakers improve to 38-32, while the 76ers fall to 38-32.
